item.title: Adult
item.description: 25th May 2007 I suddenly realize I am a machine. I do the same things everyday. I’ve stopped feeling. I’ve stopped thinking. I’m too busy with my life.

item.title: Insanity?
item.description: From May 2008 How intensely have you questioned your sanity? Today my brain perceived differently- I saw at angles I hadn’t seen before and heard at times I couldn’t explain.
